    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks. i checked the logs for the picking process and everything looks pretty clean on the paper side. no major errors or missed scans. it's just these tiny amounts disappearing constantly, almost like they are just... vanishing. if it's not theft or broken units, what else could account for such a consistent, small-scale leak in the count?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
