      "content": "we've already checked for mislabeling and dust, and the putaway scans are all verified by the floor managers. it's frustrating because it's so random yet so constant. it's like we're losing bits and pieces of the inventory to something we just can't see or track in the system. is there any other category of \"invisible\" error i'm missing? something that wouldn't show up in a standard audit?",
